will reflect the drawing

00:01:38.180 --> 00:01:41.630
across the y-axis.

00:01:41.630 --> 00:01:45.270
What will be the coordinates
of C after the reflection?

00:01:45.270 --> 00:01:47.350
So when they say reflection,
they mean, literally, just

00:01:47.350 --> 00:01:49.860
take the image of this and
you flip it over onto the

00:01:49.860 --> 00:01:50.820
right-hand side.

00:01:50.820 --> 00:01:53.260
So I could draw it out,
and draw it in blue.

00:01:53.260 --> 00:01:56.550
So if I take the reflection,
this line right here is at

00:01:56.550 --> 00:01:57.210
