00:03:01.330 --> 00:03:03.120
Maybe I could call it C prime.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:07.440
And so its coordinates are--
its x-coordinate is 2.

00:03:07.440 --> 00:03:09.830
And we're 2 to the right;
